  "body": "when account is unlocked, we can see the log:\n\n```\n2015/04/08 12:54:34 [XETH] Contract addr 05c5c33cb8c4c287ca7cfb26a4dff57a57afeb33\n```\n\nbut there is no log for failed attempt of transaction on locked account. It would be great if we could have something like:\n\n```\n2015/04/08 12:54:34 [RPC] Transaction failed. Could not unlock sender account\n```\n",
